{"tid":777213,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［整合］8/11 天星碼頭港獨革命行動報告","createTime":"2018-08-12T16:53:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-14T04:04:48.000Z","uid":43785,"like":6,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"93d076113af645b697f4e4a2e7d799570a4c806b","tid":777213,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T16:53:50.000Z","msg":"8/11 天星碼頭港獨革命行動摘名報告<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#出席     #表現<br />\n盧斯達   因有腎病，成晚安靜幫警察影相<br />\n法國閪   攞住個cam戇撚鳩鳩玩賓周<br />\n梁金城   成班廢老舉紙牌抗議，仲衰撚過民主黨<br />\n陳家駒   成晚要求警察執法，宣揚警民合作<br />\n<br />\n其他以 黃碌撚 為首嘅革命戰士及三千益友 ，全數缺席<br />\n<br />\n總結：叫人去衝自己唔衝正仆街。"},{"pid":"ad2eb07158ee6aa3d6a17f189a85592346535ba9","tid":777213,"uid":43785,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T16:54:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/13/MrAsUK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F13%2FMrAsUK.png&h=78182438&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港獨革命（老千）領袖陳家駒，搖身一變成為警察代言人，唔知嘅人真係以為佢係警察。真乖。"},{"pid":"a9bdfbb4bee3a127eb405160084e88aefa71aed9","tid":777213,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T16:54:58.000Z","msg":"今次集會開記招果個「學生獨立聯盟」陳家駒 ，係老千黎。<br />\n<br />\n事緣係2015選區議會嗰陣已經成25歲人，仲要係濕鳩老師，而家已經差唔多30歲，呢位 「呀叔」 為咗食人血饅頭呃錢叫雞吸毒，竟然厚顏無恥到走去扮「學生」，夾硬騎劫真正年青學生民意，自己唔衝但不斷出post推中小學生去死！<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/13/Presmt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F13%2FPresmt.png&h=74723dd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/13/cQCt0j.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F13%2FcQCt0j.png&h=c7b76eee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6472930a029ceaa996cc25ddedc5ea6e0b73872c","tid":777213,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T16:55:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/13/ZnlY0M.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"http